					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">It's possible to have up to 512 tiles by tweaiking $2000.4 in real time to select if the left or right pattern table is displayed.
<br />
<br />That way it's possible to change table mid-frame, and even mid-scanline (but it requires at least 2 tiles or "margin" which are shared between both tables, as I've done it <a href="http://nesdev.com/bbs/viewtopic.php?t=5468" class="postlink">here</a>).
<br />
<br />Maybe if you were telling us what exactly you're trying to do we could help more.</div>

					
